      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p>We are pleased to announce that Liferay DXP Quarterly Release 2026.Q2 is now available for download.</p>\n\n<p>The key highlights for this Quarterly Release are:</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Cloud Native AWS-Ready - <span class=\"ml-rte-link-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/e/release-notes/release-highlights/20004/27867411?r=27867411#:~:text=Cloud-,Cloud%20Native%20AWS%2Dready,-Streamline%20AWS%20Deployments\">Learn More</a></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>To learn more about all the new features available in 2026.Q2 Quarterly Release, please review the <a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/e/release-notes/release-highlights/20004/27867411?r=27867411\">Release Notes</a>, or watch the <span class=\"ml-rte-link-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://liferay.dev/b/liferay-dxp-2026-q2-release-webinar\">Release Webinar</a></span>.<br>\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://customer.liferay.com/en/downloads?p_p_id=com_liferay_osb_customer_downloads_display_web_DownloadsDisplayPortlet&amp;_com_liferay_osb_customer_downloads_display_web_DownloadsDisplayPortlet_productAssetCategoryId=122235468&amp;_com_liferay_osb_customer_downloads_display_web_DownloadsDisplayPortlet_fileTypeAssetCategoryId=122235708\">View Available Downloads</a></h3>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr>\n<p><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/anatomy-of-a-quarterly-release\"><strong><u>Anatomy of a Quarterly Release</u></strong></a><br>\nLearn more about the file and folder structures for Quarterly Releases.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/liferay-dxp-quarterly-release-process\"><strong><u>Frequently Asked Questions</u></strong></a><br>\nSee more important information about our DXP Platform versioning and release cadence.</p>\n\n<p><u><strong><a href=\"https://support.liferay.com/w/liferay-dxp-2026.q2-compatibility-matrix\">DXP 2026.Q2 Compatibility Matrix</a></strong></u><br>\nCheck compatibility here to ensure a smooth and&nbsp;supported upgrade</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://learn.liferay.com/w/dxp/self-hosted-installation-and-upgrades\"><strong><u>Installation Instructions</u></strong></a><br>\nLearn how to install DXP Quarterly Releases.</p>"
      },
